entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Sheeli was summoned and is standing next to you. Find out if she is okay.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Great work pirate! We are sending a shuttle, but you need to meet it near by. Hussle to that location and well pick her up.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Go to the shuttle extraction point with Sheeli.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Wait for the shuttle to arrive.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Was there not enough room on the shuttle? Oh well. Return to Nym for your reward.
